                <note rend="inline" type="source">868.51 Refugee Settlement Commission/64:
                    Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Special Mission at Lausanne</gloss> to
                        the <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Lausanne</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1923-06-15T18:00:00+01:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">June 15, 1923—6 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                        <lb/>[Received June 15—3:40 p.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>428. Department’s 182, June 13, 11 a.m. First meeting of Finance Committee of the
                    League of Nations will be held June 21st. I have written a letter to the
                    president of the committee in which I refer to the suggestion made to the
                    Department of State that Dolbeare is ready to attend the meetings insofar as
                    they relate to emergency relief.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Grew</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
